https://netbox.prod.infra.deposit/

  - Select "Sites"
  - Datacenter3 (If it is DC3)
  - Select "Prefixes"
  - Check on Role column to find out the required Type of the VM
    - 10.17.8.0/24 (For Test)
  - click on IP Addresses
    - There will be a list of free addresses
    - Click on the free ip and add the DNS name and Create
  - The new IP will get assigned to the desired VM
  
